description:
This week, Anna and Sim chat with the wonderfully funny Jesse Tyler Ferguson (MODERN FAMILY). They talk about painful high school theater memories (3:24), unspoken birthday problems (8:12), and play a round of deal breakers (13:00)!

Later they call Kelly (35:30) who needs help dealing with her dad who only wants to talk about politics, and Ally (51:45) who's having a problem with her fiance's family. Tune in!
